I'm pleased to report that I just passed my Ph.D. defense, which as
you know was about NEAT.  The final dissertation and defense are the
main reason my participation here has been a bit sparse lately.  It
really is grueling as the Ph.D. process comes to an end.  Anyway, I
hope to get more involved in things here again as soon as I recover :)

ken
